## UnsubscribeObject interface

An object with the `unsubscribe` method. Subscribable stores might choose to return such object instead of directly returning [UnsubscribeFunction](./ngx-tansu.unsubscribefunction.md) from a subscription call.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface UnsubscribeObject 
```
